⍝ CatenateAxis.tc
⍝ ═══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: X∊⍳(⍴⍴A)⌈⍴⍴B; axes other than X must conform
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ (⍴⍴A)⌈⍴⍴B
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 2) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      X ← 2
      Z ← A,[X]B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ (⍴⍴A)⌈⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: (⍴Z)[X] ←→ (⍴A)[X]+(⍴B)[X]
      (⍴Z)[X] ≡ (⍴A)[X]+(⍴B)[X]
1
